missionEventData.data2: In the far reaches of the Outer Rim a rebellion is forming. A rebel cell led by the frigate Redemption and ace pilot Keyan Farlander have been striking back against the evil galactic empire. But the Emperor is at the height of his power, and even now he is marshalling his forces at the edge of the mid-rim. But help has come from the most unlikely of places. The captain of an imperial corvette has sent the rebel freedom fighters a secret message, he wishes to defect...

missionEventData.data1: What we are about to do is strictly a volunteer mission, so I’d like to say thank you to Lieutenant Keyan Farlander who has agreed to undertake this mission. Using the captured Imperial Shuttle, the Lieutenant will rendezvous with the Invincible in the far quadrant of the Dellalt sector. There they will unload their cargo before departing. The bomb is timed to go off thirty seconds after your departure so make sure you clear the space around the Invincible quickly. If all goes well the disorganised Imperial fleet will retreat to the safety of the mid-rim. Good luck.
Shuttle Trydent you are cleared for hyperspace passage.

missionEventData.data3: Thanks to your efforts the Imperial fleet is in full retreat, and for the first time since the end of the Clone Wars, the Dellalt system is free. But make no mistake, this is only the beginning of our war against the Empire.

missionEventData.data1: We have you on screen now, please identify.
Shuttle Trydent, requesting permission to dock with the Invincible.
Shuttle Trydent, transmit the security code for docking authorisation.
Shuttle Trydent. Permission for docking granted. Follow your present course.
This is the Harraser to all vessels. Don't let that shuttle escape!
